<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Student Job Tracking API</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
        }

        body {
            min-height: 100vh;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #00b09b 0%, #96c93d 100%);
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            color: white;
            padding: 2rem;
        }

        .container {
            text-align: center;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 3rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
        }

        p {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            line-height: 1.6;
            opacity: 0.9;
        }

        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 1rem 2rem;
            background: white;
            color: #00b09b;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 50px;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
        }

        .btn:hover {
            transform: translateY(-3px);
            box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
            background: #f8f9fa;
        }

        .features {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 2rem;
            margin-top: 3rem;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }

        .feature {
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
            padding: 1.5rem;
            border-radius: 10px;
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            width: 250px;
        }

        .feature h3 {
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Student Job Tracking API</h1>
        <p>A comprehensive job tracking system for students with complete API documentation. Built with Express.js and Swagger.</p>
        
        <a href="/documentation" target="_blank" class="btn">View API Documentation</a>

        <div class="features">
            <div class="feature">
                <h3>Job Management</h3>
                <p>Track applications, interviews, and job status updates efficiently</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature">
                <h3>Student Profiles</h3>
                <p>Manage student information, skills, and career preferences</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature">
                <h3>Analytics</h3>
                <p>Detailed insights on application success rates and trends</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>